data.description:
Looking for a super cute and well loved home to call your own?  Well come look at this precious home. 4/1.5  Really nice home with a great layout. Kitchen has newer appliances, all new flooring throughout home, really large yard for your gatherings, kids or fur babies! There is a 4th large bedroom that was added on with the laundry room being inside as well.  The half bathroom is in one of the bedrooms : )  Entire reroute done in approx 2021!
This is a well loved older home in a nice quiet area! Make your appointment today!
